song_name: You Make It Seem Like Nothing
Battle Of Who Could Care Less
version_description: The chords for this song are not on UG (yet) and the tabs are not good in my opinion, but found the chords elsewhere and modified to be complete and without jumping around. The chord progressions should help with playing the tab(s) better. Goal is to get the song added to UG so have others can contribute to improve it. Reference the album version of the song here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Y1wm7CFRCQ.
